      "justification_correct": "COSO identifies Monitoring as an essential component ensuring controls remain effective over time. Continuous monitoring (e.g., exception reports, KRI tracking, control testing) detects control gaps before fraud occurs. This proactive approach aligns with ACFE's fraud prevention hierarchy.",
