    {
      "num": 11,
      "text": "In designing a comprehensive fraud risk management program, which sequencing of activities best aligns with the COSO framework and ACFE guidance?",
      "tag": "Fraud Risk Management & COSO Framework",
      "options": [
        "B. Implement detective controls immediately → assess fraud risks → establish policies → develop ethics programs.",
        "A. Establish tone at the top and control environment → conduct fraud risk assessment → design preventive and detective controls → implement monitoring and communication mechanisms.",
