      "correct": 3,
      "justification_correct": "COSO framework endorses risk-based decision-making: document, monitor, and accept residual risks with explicit management approval. ACFE Manual 2024 recognizes that perfect fraud prevention is economically impractical; continuous reassessment is required.",
